WEBVTT

1
00:13:30.910 --> 00:13:32.740 
这个宝座真不赖
What a glorious throne!

2
00:13:32.740 --> 00:13:35.480 
但为什么屁股下面有个洞
Why does it have a hole?

3
00:13:35.480 --> 00:13:40.350 
唔  人类喜欢把东西放进去然后冲掉
Um, humans put things in there and flush 'em down.

4
00:13:40.350 --> 00:13:42.050 
冲掉  怎么冲
Flush? What's a flush?

5
00:13:44.620 --> 00:13:47.950 
我的天  水都被冲到哪去了
My word, where does the water go?

6
00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:50.360 
谁也不知道
Nobody knows.

7
00:13:50.360 --> 00:13:54.460 
这可是地球最大的未解奥秘之一
It's one of Earth's greatest mysteries.

8
00:13:54.460 --> 00:13:56.430 
这个也能放进去吗
Does this go in it?

9
00:13:56.430 --> 00:13:57.960 
是的哦
All the time.

